org.hibernate.testing.junit5.dynamictests

Annotation Type DynamicOrder


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Inherited
public @interface DynamicOrder
    Specifies the order in which tests will be sorted and executed.

    This is based on Junit 5.4's @Order annotation.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      int value
      The order value for annotated element.

    • Element Detail

      • value

        public abstract int value
        The order value for annotated element.

        The elements are ordered based on priority where a lower value has greater priority than a higher value. For example, Integer.MAX_VALUE has the lowest priority.

        Default:
        2147483647
